    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Dorsal habitus of– A) Pheropsophus devagiriensis sp. nov. (Male, ‘India: Tamil Nadu: Courtallam’, Holotype), B) P. indicus sp. nov. (Male, ‘India: Kerala: Palakkad’, Holotype)" ;
